For An Act To Be Entitled
14
15 AN ACT TO AMEND THE LAW CONCERNING PROHIBITED
16 CONTRACTS BY STATE AGENCIES; TO PROHIBIT THE USE OF
17 PUBLIC FUNDS BY STATE AGENCIES TO PURCHASE
18 PROMOTIONAL ITEMS MADE IN CHINA; AND FOR OTHER
19 PURPOSES.
